reviewText: great series , I am so happy I am able to watch it again and again, very good quality dvd's.
Yes it did all 6 seasons were awesome & it was really cool to see how they end it  but only i did not like was there is no episode Guide with it
When are you going to get in the whole series????!!!!!!  Having to buy the series individually is VERY expensive. but I want it for my wife who is a great fan of Brooke Elliott

I bought this locally and I absolutely love it!! A model who does nothing but waste her time dies and comes back to life in a BBW's body.

So she gets a first hand "look" at what its like to have said body while still having the mind like a model and with a touch of lawyer added to the mix.

This is a funny informative tv series!!
Had more fun watching this series! It was a marathon. Really enjoyed!
I loved season 1-4. Seasons 5 and 6 were  convoluted and horrible. Disappointing.
so funny, great clean show, wished she had sung more in it :)

Very good box set. No problem with the shipping. It actually arrived earlier than planned.

For those who want to have a look at what the package looks like, here are some detailed pictures.

The DVDs are the same as the ones in the individual seasons. The menus are the same - meaning the last ones (those of Seasons 5 and 6) are plain and blue... Just so you know: there is no episode guide inside the box.

With so many discs that could be flawed, I was very pleased with the extremely good quality of each and every disc.  Drop Dead Diva is my all time favorite of TV shows.  I am overweight and it was good to not only see an overweight main character but the fact that she had many men interested in her despite her weight.  She had many...I had one :)

glad to have the whole series on dvd  wish they would now bring out the mysteries of laura . Drop dead diva was a very good series with a lot of good acting by all even some great guest stars like liza Minnelli  5 stars
I love watching Drop Dead Diva. I especially like watching it whenever I feel like it...as they took it off TV.
